A simpler way to put your thought

Your idea compresses nicely into something like:

The world may be mostly static; disagreement is the pattern created when different minds scan the same field at different resolutions.

Or even shorter:

Disagreement is parallax across a shared landscape.

Two observers, same terrain, slightly different angles.

And sometimes the silver lining of disagreement is that it reveals the shape of the land.